content.text:
- **Carrick Therapeutics — “CDK12/13 Inhibitor” (pipeline page)**
  - URL: `https://www.carricktherapeutics.com/pipeline/cdk1213-inhibitor`
  - Direct quotes:
    - “**CT7439: CDK12/13 inhibitor/Cyclin-K Degrader**”
    - “**CT7439 is a CDK12/13/Cyclin-K degrader**”
    - “The compound acts as an inhibitor of **CDK12** but also as a ‘**glue degrader**’ of **Cyclin-K**”

- **Carrick Therapeutics (Press Release) — “Carrick Therapeutics Announces First Patient Dosed in Phase 1 Clinical Trial of CT7439 (CDK12/13 Inhibitor)”**
  - URL: `https://www.carricktherapeutics.com/investors/news-events/press-releases/detail/25/carrick-therapeutics-announces-first-patient-dosed-in-phase`
  - Direct quotes:
    - “evaluating **CT7439**, a novel … **(CDK12/13) inhibitor / Cyclin-K glue-degrader**”
    - “Clinical trial details can also be found on www.clinicaltrials.gov under study ID: **NCT06600789**.”

- **Clinical Trials Registry (ICH GCP) — “A Modular Phase 1/2 Study With CT7439 in Participants With Solid Malignancies”**
  - URL: `https://ichgcp.net/clinical-trials-registry/NCT06600789`
  - Direct quotes:
    - “Intervention / Treatment  * Drug: **CT7439 Capsules (0.5 mg, 1mg, 3mg)**”
    - “#### Sponsor  **Carrick Therapeutics Limited**”
    - “#### Study Start (Actual)  **August 16, 2024**”

- **PubMed — “Therapeutic Targeting of CDK12/CDK13 in Triple-Negative Breast Cancer”**
  - URL: `https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31668947/`
  - Direct quotes:
    - “development of **SR-4835**, a highly selective dual inhibitor of **CDK12** and **CDK13**, which disables **triple-negative breast cancer (TNBC)** cells.”

- **PMC (J Med Chem) — “Discovery of ZLC491 as a Potent, Selective, and Orally Bioavailable CDK12/13 PROTAC Degrader”**
  - URL: `https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC11513923/`
  - Direct quotes:
    - “discovery of **ZLC491** as a potent, selective, and orally bioavailable **CDK12/13 PROTAC degrader**.”
    - “degraded **CDK12** and **CDK13** … in **TNBC MDA-MB-231** cells.”

- **PubMed — “Noncovalent CDK12/13 dual inhibitors-based PROTACs…”**
  - URL: `https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/34864331/`
  - Direct quotes:
    - “we have synthesized a potent **PROTAC degrader PP-C8** based on the noncovalent dual inhibitors of **CDK12/13**”
    - “**PP-C8** demonstrates … effects with **PARP inhibitor** in **triple-negative breast cancer (TNBC)**.”

- **PubMed — “Discovery of a Highly Potent and Selective Dual PROTAC Degrader of CDK12 and CDK13”**
  - URL: `https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/35938508/`
  - Direct quotes:
    - “dual **CDK12/13 degraders** by employing the **proteolysis-targeting chimera (PROTAC)** technology.”
    - “The optimal **compound 7f** effectively degraded **CDK12** and **CDK13**”
    - “inhibited proliferation of multiple **TNBC** cell lines”

- **PubMed — “Discovery of novel imidazo[1,2-b]pyridazine derivatives as potent covalent inhibitors of CDK12/13”**
  - URL: `https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/39955845/`
  - Direct quotes:
    - “Triple-negative breast cancer (**TNBC**)… cyclin-dependent kinases 12/13 (**CDK12/13**)”
    - “Among these compounds, **compound 24** emerged as the most potent inhibitor”
    - “superior efficacy … covalent inhibitor, **THZ531**.”

- **PubMed — “Discovery of a molecular glue promoting CDK12-DDB1 interaction to trigger cyclin K degradation”**
  - URL: `https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32804079/`
  - Direct quotes:
    - “a new molecular glue **HQ461**”
    - “**HQ461** acts by promoting an interaction between **CDK12** and **DDB1-CUL4-RBX1** E3 ubiquitin ligase”
    - “A provisional patent application (**PCT/CN2020/095482**) has been filed for the application of **HQ461** as molecular glues regulating **CDK12-DDB1** interaction to degrade **CCNK**.”
